6.3 Limitations and Critical Assessment

While the NGSSM-DS v4.0 framework represents a significant advance, several limitations must be acknowledged:

6.3.1 Experimental Validation Gap

This thesis is a blueprint, not an experimental validation. The property data presented (e.g., 600 MPa yield strength for PSM-1, 450 MPa for PSM-1B) are targets based on computational modeling and literature analogs, not measured values. Key uncertainties include:

Claim Basis Uncertainty
